  "overview": {
    "zh": "香蕉振动筛采用多段式弧形筛面，入料端倾角30-45°，出料端0-5°。处理能力60-600m³/h，筛面面积1.8-3.6m²，适用于5-80mm物料。差动式激振器确保高含泥量湿物料顺畅筛分，适用于高难度选矿作业。",
    "en": "Banana Vibrating Screen features multi-section arc design with 30-45° feed end and 0-5° discharge end inclination. Capacity 60-600m³/h, screen area 1.8-3.6m², for 5-80mm particles. Differential exciter ensures smooth screening of wet materials with high clay content, ideal for challenging mineral processing."
  },
